content:
Feather usually refers to Feather, dropped by Chickens and used in the Fletching and Fishing skills.

However, it may also refer to:

Quest items[edit | edit source]

  • Bronze feather, used in the Eagles' Peak quest
  • Eagle feather, used in the Eagles' Peak quest
  • Feathered journal, used in the Eagles' Peak quest
  • Golden feather, used in the Eagles' Peak quest
  • Golden feather (Priest in Peril), used in the Priest in Peril quest
  • Griffin feather, used in the Grim Tales quest
  • Magic gold feather, used in the Holy Grail quest
  • Metal feather, used in the Eagles' Peak quest
  • Phoenix feather, used in the The Golem quest
  • Silver feather, used in the Eagles' Peak quest

Other[edit | edit source]

  • Blue feather, dropped by Cerulean twitches
  • Fire feather, a drop from the Entrana firebird used in the Heroes' Quest
  • Orange feather, a drop from Copper longtails
  • Red feather, a drop from Crimson swifts
  • Stripy feather, a drop from Tropical wagtails
  • Yellow feather, a drop from Golden warblers
 This page is used to distinguish between articles with similar names.

'''Feather''' usually refers to [[Feather]], dropped by [[Chickens]] and used in the [[Fletching]] and [[Fishing]] skills.

However, it may also refer to:
